				<a href="https://help.servmask.com/knowledgebase/how-to-add-import-and-export-capabilities-to-wordpress-users/" target="_blank">Détails techniques</a>','To choose a file please go inside the link and click on the browse button.'=>'Pour choisir un fichier, veuillez suivre le lien et cliquer sur le bouton Parcourir.','Finish'=>'Terminer','Please ensure your file was created with the All-in-One WP Migration plugin.
